<h2 class="section-title hidden stagger-1">Plate Reverb — EMT 140</h2>
<p class="section-desc hidden stagger-2">The EMT 140, introduced in 1957, is a large steel plate (2m × 1m) suspended by springs in a frame. A transducer drives vibrations into the plate; pickups capture the result. Click the plate to excite it.</p>
