<!-- PRE-DELAY -->
<section class="section" id="predelay">
<p class="section-label hidden">Section 04</p>
<h2 class="section-title hidden stagger-1">Pre-Delay — The Singer and the Wall</h2>
<p class="section-desc hidden stagger-2">Pre-delay is the gap between the dry signal and the first reverb reflection. It creates perceptual separation — the brain hears the direct sound clearly before the reverberant wash begins.</p>
